6. Xavfsizlik (Security Architecture)
6.1. Tahdid modeli (Threat Model)
Loyihaga oid asosiy tahdidlar va ulardan himoya:
Tahdid	Ehtimollik	Zarar	Himoya
Kassir tan narx ko'rib raqobatchilarga sotadi	Yuqori	O'rta	DB-level RLS, hech qachon API'da qaytarilmaydi
Kassir refund qilib pul o'g'irlaydi	Yuqori	Yuqori	Kuniga 3 marta limit, summa limit, admin tasdiq
Tenant ma'lumotlari boshqa tenantga leak	O'rta	Kritik	RLS + integratsion testlar
IMEI bazasi o'g'irlanadi	Past	Yuqori	AES-256 encryption, audit log
Brute-force PIN'ga	Yuqori	O'rta	Rate limit 5/15min, account lock
Telegram bot token leak	O'rta	Yuqori	Vault'da saqlash, har 90 kun rotatsiya
DDoS hujum	Past	O'rta	Cloudflare avtomatik
SQL injection	Past	Kritik	Drizzle ORM (parameterized)
XSS	Past	O'rta	React avtomatik escape + CSP
CSRF	Past	O'rta	Better Auth same-site cookies
Insecure deserialization	Past	O'rta	Zod validation har endpoint'da
Xavfsizlik update'lari yo'q	Yuqori	Yuqori	Dependabot avtomatik
6.2. Authentication (Kirim) Strategiyasi
Admin kirimi:
•Email + password (Argon2id hashing)
•2FA majburiy — Telegram orqali kod
•Brute-force himoya: 5 urinish → 15 daqiqa lock
•Yangi qurilmadan kirim → email + Telegram'ga xabar
•Sessiya 24 soat, refresh token 7 kun
Kassir kirimi:
•Telefon raqami + 6-raqamli PIN (bcrypt cost 12)
•Faqat ro'yxatdan o'tgan qurilmadan kira oladi (device fingerprint)
•PIN noto'g'ri 5 marta → admin'ga xabar, account lock
•Smena ochilganidan keyin sessiya aktiv
•Smena yopilganda sessiya yopiladi
•8 soat ishlamasdan turish → avtomatik chiqib ketadi
6.3. Authorization (Ruxsatlar) — RBAC + RLS
Rollar:
Rol	Tavsif
super_admin	Anthropic ichki — barcha tenant'larga kirish (faqat support uchun)
tenant_owner	Tenant egasi — to'liq ruxsat o'z tenant ichida
admin	Tenant ichida operatsion boshqaruv
manager	Tahlil va hisobot, ba'zi operatsiyalar
accountant	Moliyaviy boshqaruv, qarzlar
warehouse	Ombor operatsiyalari
cashier	Faqat sotuv va asosiy operatsiyalar
RLS (Row Level Security) misol:
-- Faqat o'z tenant'idagi ma'lumotni ko'rsatadi
CREATE POLICY tenant_isolation ON sales
  FOR ALL
  USING (tenant_id = current_setting('app.tenant_id')::uuid);

-- Kassir tan narxni KO'RA OLMAYDI (column-level)
CREATE POLICY no_cost_price_for_cashier ON products
  FOR SELECT
  USING (
    CASE WHEN current_setting('app.user_role') = 'cashier'
    THEN cost_price IS NULL  -- API'da bu ustun NULL bo'lib qaytadi
    ELSE TRUE
    END
  );

-- Audit log'ni hech kim o'zgartira/o'chira olmaydi
CREATE POLICY immutable_audit ON audit_logs
  FOR UPDATE USING (FALSE);
CREATE POLICY immutable_audit_delete ON audit_logs
  FOR DELETE USING (FALSE);
6.4. Ma'lumotlarni shifrlash
At-rest (saqlanganda):
•PostgreSQL — Supabase tomonidan AES-256 encryption
•Sensitive ustunlar (IMEI, passport, telefon) — application-level AES-256
•Kalit Supabase Vault'da saqlanadi
In-transit (uzatilganda):
•HTTPS (TLS 1.3) majburiy — HTTP redirect
•HSTS header (max-age 1 yil)
•Internal API'lar uchun ham TLS
6.5. Audit Log — barcha kritik amallar
Quyidagi amallar avtomatik ravishda audit_logs jadvaliga yoziladi:
•Login/logout (muvaffaqiyatli va muvaffaqiyatsiz)
•Sotuv yaratish, refund, bekor qilish
•Mahsulot narxini o'zgartirish
•Foydalanuvchi qo'shish/o'chirish/rolini o'zgartirish
•Qarzni o'chirish yoki o'zgartirish
•Smena ochish/yopish
•Settings o'zgartirish
•Telegram/SMS sozlamalari o'zgartirish
Audit log immutable qilib qo'yiladi:
-- PostgreSQL trigger
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION prevent_audit_changes()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$
BEGIN
  RAISE EXCEPTION 'Audit log o''zgartirib bo''lmaydi';
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

CREATE TRIGGER audit_immutable
BEFORE UPDATE OR DELETE ON audit_logs
FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION prevent_audit_changes();
6.6. Refund firibgarligidan himoya
Klassik POS firibgarligi: kassir mavjud bo'lmagan refund yaratib, kassadan pul oladi. Himoya:
6.Kassir kuniga max 3 marta refund qila oladi
7.Bir refund max 200,000 so'm
8.Bundan ko'p — admin Telegram'ga so'rov boradi, qabul kerak
9.Har refund — audit log + Telegram xabari
10.Refund'da original sotuv ID majburiy (mavjud bo'lmagan refund mumkin emas)
11.Bir sotuv max 1 marta refund qilinadi (qisman bo'lsa, ko'p marta)
12.Anomaly detection: kassir kuniga >5 refund — admin'ga alert
